data.description: 9+ acres! Rustic, hidden, peaceful, & private describe this home which features a combination of woods and meadows.  Only 30 mins from the Indianapolis airport, this property has several updates including all new vinyl-plank flooring through-out.  Walk out basement is fantastic for entertaining inside and out and a raised gardening area for those green thumb enthusiast.  Energy efficient geothermal HVAC which maintains super low utility bills all year long.  The 4 appliance packaged will stay with property, fireplace & pellet stove in home just compliments the geothermal system to make this property just that much cozier. The entire home is 100% electric with city water, 40X60 garage with lean too for your tractor plus a concrete workshop. Wildlife abundant, many deer are harvested from this property each year. Additional fenced in area for your livestock is also available to the new owners!
